0.3.0
- Refactor: split core API and versioner into `server/core_api.lua` and `server/versioner.lua`
- API change: event-only delivery via `cz-core:ready` and `cz-core:request_api` (no global/export `GetCore`)
- Feature: Versioner compares local `version` file with repo `version` (supports raw.githubusercontent & Contents API)
- Docs: README updated with RPC and Versioner usage examples
